### Subscribe with a new email (will send confirmation email with token)
POST http://localhost:5000/api/subscribe
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "email": "ms_abaziz@esi.dz"
}

###

# ⚠️ After this request, check your server logs or email inbox for the confirmation link.
# It will look like: http://localhost:5000/api/confirm?token=abcd1234
# Copy-paste that token below to simulate the confirmation step.

### Confirm subscription (replace TOKEN_VALUE with the token you got in email/logs)
GET http://localhost:5000/api/confirm?token=TOKEN_VALUE

###

### Add a news article (will only be sent to verified subscribers)
POST http://localhost:5000/api/news
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "title": "Demo Project Launched",
  "content": "This is a demo news article for the newsletter."
}

###

### (Optional) Check list of subscribers (for debugging)
GET http://localhost:5000/api/subscribers
